		<h3 class="author-profile-header">About the Author:</h3>
		<h4 class="author-name fn n"><a href="http://blissfullydomestic.com/author/kathyfriend/" title="Posts by Kathy Friend">Kathy Friend</a></h4>
		<p class="author-description author-bio">
			Kathy Friend, wardrobe coach and personal shopper, is Fashion and Style Expert on the WSBT TV Morning Show (CBS affiliate), Fashion Editor of Michiana FAMILY Magazine, and Wedding Day Magazine.  Kathy peddles women's clothing for 2 designers, a private label (direct to customer), and a boutique collection called Madras 641.

Kathy's expertise is in fit and style.  Extensive training she has had as an employee of several apparel companies gives her a unique perspective and insight to making women look their very best.<br/>
			<a href="http://www.kathyfriend.com">Kathy Friend's Website</a>
		</p>
	</div>

			
